---
title: "Sequence Diagram - Option 4: Show Adjusted Salary Workers"
config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant V as WorkerView
    participant C as WorkerController
    participant M as Management

    User->>V: select option 4
    V-->>C: choice = 4
    C->>M: getInfomationSalary()
    M->>M: sort salaryHistories by worker id
    M-->>C: return List~SalaryHistory~
    C->>V: displaySalaryHistories(list)

    alt list is empty
        V->>User: "No worker has been adjusted salary."
    else list has data
        V->>User: show table (code, name, salary before, amount, status UP/DOWN, salary after, time)
    end

    C->>V: back to main screen
    V->>User: display menu (1-5)
